1.5** | 模板市场，批量处理优化，成本优化 | 2 周 |\n| **v2.0** | 高级编辑功能，多平台发布集成 | 待定 |\n\n---\n\n*本技术设计文档由 spec-code-team 架构师墨子制定，所有开发工作应遵循上述设计规范。*\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"qwen3-max","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":19763,"output":9165,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":28928,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772587084140}}
